### Get All Orders
GET {{Microservice.Order.Api_HostAddress}}/v1/orders
Accept: application/json

###

### Create Order
POST {{Microservice.Order.Api_HostAddress}}/v1/orders
Authorization:Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  
  "address": {
    "province": "Istanbul",
    "city": "Kadikoy",
    "region": "Marmara",
    "street": "Caferaga Mahallesi, Moda Caddesi No:123",
    "postalCode": "34710"
  },
  "payment": {
    "cardName": "John Doe",
    "cardNumber": "4532015112830366",
    "expiration": "12/25",
    "cvv": "123",
    "amount": 5000
  },
  "orders": [
    {
      "productId": "{{productId1}}",
      "productName": "ASP.NET Core Course",
      "unitPrice": 200
    },
    {
      "productId": "{{productId2}}",
      "productName": "Microservices Course",
      "unitPrice": 300
    }
  ]
}

###

### Create Order - Multiple Items
POST {{Microservice.Order.Api_HostAddress}}/v1/orders
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "discount": 100,
  "address": {
    "province": "Ankara",
    "city": "Cankaya",
    "region": "Central Anatolia",
    "street": "Kizilirmak Mahallesi, Dumlupinar Bulvari No:45",
    "postalCode": "06510"
  },
  "payment": {
    "cardName": "Jane Smith",
    "cardNumber": "5425233430109903",
    "expiration": "06/27",
    "cvv": "456",
